  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 : \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 30 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bset on fire in Trichy camp: 30 Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bwho tried to commit suicide admitted to hospital",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Sri Lankan Tamil has caught fire at the Trichy Central Jail Special Camp and is being treated at the Trichy Government Hospital.",
        "Refugees from Sri Lanka, Bangladesh, Russia and Bulgaria are being held in special camps at the Trichy Central Jail.",
        "As a result, some Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bhave been on a hunger strike since May 20, demanding their release after more than three years in prison.",
        "As a result, 21 Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bin the camp have been on a series of hunger strikes demanding their release.",
        "Thirty Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bin a special camp tried to commit suicide by taking pills.",
        "Police rescued 30 people and admitted them to the hospital for treatment. There they are being treated. The incident has caused a great stir in the Trichy refugee camp.",
        "The Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bthere said that we were serving more than 3 years in prison and that the Tamil Nadu government and the district administration should release them.",
        "But there was no agreement on that. Meanwhile 4 Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bsuddenly climbed a tree and engaged in a struggle. They sat in the tree for a while chanting, then went downstairs."
      ],
